dct_title_s: The southern part of Lake Tanganyika (Lake Liemba of Dr. Livingstone) from a survey by Mr. Edw. C. Hore, Master Mariner, of the London Missionary Society
dct_description_sm: Villages and caravan routes along lake shore are shown. Compass declination at southern end of lake and in Ufipa territory is given. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. From: Proceedings of the Royal Geographical Society and monthly record of geography. Vol. 4 (1882), no. 1, pp. 1-28; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J6873
